Ackerman, appellant, and Blauvelt, respondent. Decree affirmed upon the grounds stated by the Vice-Chancellor in his opinion, reported in 8 O. E. Oreen 496.

Eor affirmance — Beasley, C. J., Bedle, Clement, Green, Lathrop, Lilly, Van Syckel, Wales, Woodhull. 9.

Eor reversal — Dalrimple, Scudder. 2.
